      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specification, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and a 6-speed manual Getrag transmission. The powertrain delivers a linear torque curve and a 7,900 RPM redline, supported by a recently serviced VANOS system to ensure precise variable valve timing. The chassis has been enhanced with subframe reinforcement plates, addressing a known E46 weak point, and retains its factory-spec limited-slip M Differential for optimal corner-exit traction. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the mechanical components are dialed in for peak lateral acceleration and throttle response.",
